Package: tradeplotr
Type: Package
Title: Generate Customizable Interactive Performance Reports for Financial Assets
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person(
    given = "Hugo",
    family = "Rzepian Teixeira",
    email = "hugorteixeira@senhormercado.com.br",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Hugo Rzepian Teixeira [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Hugo Rzepian Teixeira <hugorteixeira@senhormercado.com.br>
Description: R library for interactive trading and backtesting reports in HTML,
    JSON, PNG, and JPG formats. Supports xts series, quantstrat portfolios, and
    native backtest objects with return, trade, cost, position, and market data.
    Includes performance tables, cumulative and rolling returns, drawdowns,
    rolling correlations, grouped return lines, risk normalization, candlestick
    charts, trade markers, and custom themes.
